Prashant Singh is an Indian Music Director, composer, singer-songwriter, music producer, musician. Prashant singh's works are noted for integrating Indian classical music with Bollywood music, world music and traditional music arrangements.
He's Done Bollywood Movies 
1-Hum Do Anjane (27 May 2011)
2-Karle Pyar Karle (17 Jan 2014)
3-The Untold Story Aahinsa (20 Jun 2014)
4-Shallu Ki Shadi (08 Dec 2017)
5-Raagani Upcoming International Film
